description:
VOS7 2701d3f
For this query I get:

Virtuoso 42000 Error The estimated execution time 881833 (sec) exceeds the limit of 80000 (sec).

SPARQL query:
PREFIX s: <http://schema.org/>
PREFIX gr: <http://purl.org/goodrelations/v1#>
PREFIX gml: <http://www.opengis.net/ont/gml#>
PREFIX adms: <http://www.w3.org/ns/adms#>
PREFIX skos: <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#>
CONSTRUCT {
 ?kontrola s:geo ?c ;
      s:title ?objectName;
      s:description ?desc.
?c s:latitude ?lat; s:longitude ?lng .
}
FROM <http://linked.opendata.cz/resource/dataset/coi.cz/kontroly-sankce-zakazy>
FROM <http://linked.opendata.cz/resource/dataset/geocoordinates/google/schema.org>
FROM <http://linked.opendata.cz/resource/dataset/ares/or>
WHERE {
?kontrola a s:CheckAction ;
      s:location ?address ;
      s:location/s:geo ?c ;
      s:object ?object.
?object adms:identifier/skos:notation ?ic .
OPTIONAL {?object gr:legalName ?objectName .}
?c s:longitude ?lng;
        s:latitude ?lat .
?address s:streetAddress ?street;
              s:addressLocality ?locality;
              s:postalCode ?psc .
BIND (CONCAT('<a href="', ?object, '">', COALESCE(CONCAT(?ic, ': ', ?objectName), ?ic), '</a>\n', ?street, '\n', ?psc, ' ', ?locality) as ?desc)
}
It takes about 10-20 seconds to execute (when I set the estimation limit above 900 000 seconds)
